data.enText: the state of being an adult

tr: the state (and responsibilities) of a person who has attained maturity
the period of time in your life after your physical growth has stopped and you are fully developed

value.def: Adulthood is the state of being an adult.

example.ex: Few people nowadays are able to maintain friendships into adulthood.
example.tran: 如今很少有人能将友谊维持到成年。
